{"tid":1946935,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王喜寸警方多普通話同業","createTime":"2020-03-28T03:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T04:40:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fdaefc6f5bed20f7dbc46137335459b7b1eed920","tid":1946935,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200328/Q4CRVNDYEKMYUX564A74V2YV6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200328%2FQ4CRVNDYEKMYUX564A74V2YV6M%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fpX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=6d830e18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200328%2FQ4CRVNDYEKMYUX564A74V2YV6M%2F&h=da615262\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200328/Q4CRVNDYEKMYUX564A74V2YV6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n王喜寸警方多普通話同業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200328/large/1585318056_840b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200328%2Flarge%2F1585318056_840b.jpg&h=e40735d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王喜一人分飾三角，更學足PK鄧的語氣說話。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n王喜於昨日播出的《頭條新聞》 環節《驚訊》中，再次以「忠勇毅」的身份寸爆警方權利無限，卻獨欠「選舉領袖」，他說︰「今日我就為咗你彈出嚟選。」他飾演1號候選人，承諾會訓斥警務人員別再當街用普通話鬧男同業，要他以後只能「使用本地語言」，釋除大家有武警駐港的疑慮，他又寸爆說︰「香港點會有四千位操普通話的同業咁多？」<br />\n<br />\n王喜之後再分飾多角，出現在「首領選舉論壇」中，他學足警務處處長鄧炳強的語氣說︰「我絕對唔會用納稅人嘅錢，打斷香港人嘅手、腳或未來。」又指絕不會訓練警員用胡椒噴霧，更指自己政綱是︰「講香港人話 ，聽香港人話。」節目結束前，他呼籲戴手帶家居隔離人士不要周圍走，勞煩一眾手足「捉佢哋」。<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰祖李"},{"pid":"e4a715d1d307a6270d9b2cddd67073eb3318c68e","tid":1946935,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"159b882ce55d7c1b76d591c1495c14a4e74d3887","tid":1946935,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:07:50.000Z","msg